@* i18n (i18n_2): every component gets the shared string localizer as `L`. Look strings up by key —
   L["Nav.Catalog"] for text, L["Catalog.Field.Slug.Tip"] for the control's tooltip. English values live in
   Resources/SharedResource.resx; a culture's overrides in Resources/SharedResource.<culture>.resx. *@
@inject IStringLocalizer<SharedResource> L
